ty engagement is fragmented"]},{"type":"text_with_bullets","heading":null,"description":"The Community Radio & Local News Contribution Platform aims to:","bullets":["Enable citizens to report local news and events","Provide verification mechanisms for authenticity","Allow publishing via digital and community radio formats","Build a trusted hyperlocal media ecosystem"],"text":"This platform promotes community participation, transparency, and local awareness."}]},{"type":"LinkedText","data":[{"name":"Unified Mentor","url":"https://www.unifiedmentor.com"},{"name":"Press Information Bureau – Official news dissemination and media updates","url":"https://www.pib.gov.in/indexd.aspx?reg=3&lang=1"},{"name":"Community Radio Association of India – Supports community radio initiatives","url":"https://craindia.in/cra-activities/"},{"name":"• United Nations Educational Scientific and Cultural Organization – Promotes media literacy and community communication","url":"https://www.unesco.org/en"}]},{"type":"text_with_bullets","heading":"Problem Statement","description":null,"bullets":["Lack of reliable hyperlocal news sources","Limited citizen participation in journalism","Difficulty verifying user-generated content","Fragmented local communication channels","Low visibility of community issues"]},{"type":"text_with_bullets","heading":"Primary Objectives","description":null,"bullets":["Enable citizens to contribute local news","Provide verification and moderation mechanisms","Promote community radio integration","Increase awareness of local issues","Build a trusted local news platform"]},{"type":"text_with_bullets","heading":"Secondary Objectives","description":null,"bullets":["Encourage citizen journalism","Promote media literacy","Support local communities","Improve civic engagement"]},{"type":"text_with_bullets_heading","heading":"Scope of the Product","description":null,"step":[{"type":"text_with_bullets","heading":"In Scope (Phase 1)","description":null,"bullets":["User registra